headline: CBOE- A Way to Capitalize on Active Trading Now, Volatility Later
summary: New platforms, lower barriers, and new products make it easier for regular folks to speculate. One long-term beneficiary will be CBOE Global Markets Inc. (CBOE), observes Bill Patalon, chief stock picker at Stock Picker’s Corner.

headline: Did Cboe's (CBOE) Australian Listing Approval Just Reshape Its Global Exchange Ambitions?
summary: Cboe Global Markets has received regulatory approval from the Australian Securities & Investments Commission to operate a stock listings market in Australia, enabling it to compete directly with ASX Ltd. for initial public offerings. This milestone advances Cboe’s international expansion and is expected to increase choices for Australian investors while challenging the dominance of the country’s primary exchange.
